      <title>波兰亿万富翁索洛兹在继承权之争中遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/polish-billionaire-solorz-suffers-setback-in-media-empire-succession-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰亿万富翁齐格蒙特·索洛兹 (Zygmunt Solorz) 在其媒体、电信和能源帝国的继承权争夺战中遭受打击，因为列支敦士登法院在 10 月份的一项裁决中站在了他的子女一边。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/polish-billionaire-solorz-suffers-setback-in-media-empire-succession-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 11:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
